<% @title = 'Subscribe to Sitefoil' %>


<div class="container" style="margin-top:40px;">


<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3"></div>
  <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6">

<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
   <h2> Sign Up As A Beta Tester</h2>

  </div>

  <div class="panel-body" id="mc_embed_signup">
     <form action="//sitefoil.us9.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=0c7306c7e7d6fa0ba3cb6607e&amp;id=13e46db7d6" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
     <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll">
     <div class="indicates-required"><span class="asterisk">*</span> indicates required</div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="mce-EMAIL">Email Address  <span class="asterisk">*</span>
		</label>
		<input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="required email form-control" id="mce-EMAIL">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
       <label for="mce-FNAME">First Name </label>
	<input type="text" value="" name="FNAME" class="form-control" id="mce-FNAME">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
       	<label for="mce-LNAME">Last Name </label>
		<input type="text" value="" name="LNAME" class="form-control" id="mce-LNAME">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
       	<label for="mce-WEBSITE">Website URL  <span class="asterisk">*</span>
		</label>
		<input type="url" value="" name="WEBSITE" class="required url form-control" id="mce-WEBSITE">
      </div>
     
      <div id="mce-responses" class="clear">
      	<div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div>
		<div class="response" id="mce-success-response" style="display:none"></div>
      </div>
       <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
    	<div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;"><input type="text" name="b_0c7306c7e7d6fa0ba3cb6607e_13e46db7d6" tabindex="-1" value=""></div>
       <div class="form-group">
       <div class="clear"><input type="submit" value="Sign Up" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="btn btn-primary"></div>
      </div>


  </div>
  </form>
  </div>
 
 <div class="panel-footer">
 <p>Over the next coming months we will be reaching out to a limited number of users who show interest in becoming Sitefoil beta testers.</p>

 <p>We will never share your information and we will not email you things we know you don't care about.</p>

 <p>To help us prioritize (since we are starting off small), we need to know what website you intend to test with so we know what potential traffic volume we will be dealing with.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3"></div>
</div></div>
<div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

<% content_for :body_class, "form" %>
